title: Whalen, Augustus need to get going for Lynx in WNBA Finals
text:
> Indiana Whalen, Augustus need to get going for Lynx in WNBA Finals Indiana Fever’s Briann January cheers her team after she fouled out in the second half in Game 1 of the WNBA basketball finals against the Minnesota Lynx, Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, in Minneapolis. The Fever won 75-69. (AP Photo/Jim Mone) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
